SENATE RESOLUTION 285
By Akbari
A RESOLUTION to confirm the appointment of Dwayne
Thompson to the Tennessee Ethics
Commission.
WHEREAS, pursuant to Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 3-6-103, Speaker of the
Senate Randy McNally has selected Dwayne Thompson of Shelby County from a list of
candidates submitted by the Democratic Caucus of the Senate as his appointee to the
Tennessee Ethics Commission; and
WHEREAS, Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 3-6-103, requires the Senate to
confirm such appointment by a two-thirds (2/3) vote; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE ONE HUNDRED FOURTEENTH
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, that the Senate hereby confirms the
appointment of Dwayne Thompson to a four-year term on the Tennessee Ethics Commission,
such term to expire on January 1, 2030.
